<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-11-30T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-11-30T10:00:00-05:00" n="1430" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1430">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The</hi>
                            <gloss type="from">
                                <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State</hi>
                            </gloss>
                            <hi rend="italic">to the Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CJL1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Caldwell</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-30T10:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 30, 1915, 10 a. m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Your November 26, 3 p. m. Your action in withdrawing protection of German
                            and Turkish interests approved. Department cannot approve permitting
                            German subjects or any nationals other than Americans remaining in the
                            Legation or taking refuge therein except they be in immediate danger of
                            their lives.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>